OL,7,FA new exhibition that aims to
OL,8,Fcelebrate the vibrant culture of
OL,9,FGypsy, Roma and Traveller artists is
OL,10,Falso working to raise awareness of the
OL,11,Fdiscrimination faced by members of
OL,12,Fthese communities.
OL,14,FThe Romani Cultural & Arts Company
OL,15,F(RCAC) has launched the latest edition
OL,16,Fof their Gypsy Makers project - a
OL,17,Ftouring exhibition that features work
OL,18,Ffrom artists that the RCAC has
OL,19,Fcommissioned since the inception of
OL,20,Fthe Gypsy Maker initiative 10 years
OL,21,Fago in 2014.
