OL,3,C'We have a vibrant culture but it's
OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,FIt aims to continue to challenge pre-
OL,8,Fconceptions by increasing knowledge
OL,9,Fand public awareness of the dynamic,
OL,10,Flong-standing heritage of artistic
OL,11,Fendeavour and creativity within Gypsy,
OL,12,FRoma & Traveller communities.
OL,14,FIsaac Blake is the founder and
OL,15,FExecutive Director of then RCAC and
OL,16,Fexplained how it can be a "challenge
OL,17,Fto get venues that are inclusive of
OL,18,FGypsy, Roma and Travellers."
