OL,3,C'We have a vibrant culture but it's
OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,FHe continued: "People often say we
OL,8,Fdidn't realise that you could have
OL,9,Fthis sort of quality of work because
OL,10,Fthe assumption is so low.
OL,12,F"The only challenge that I receive is
OL,13,Factually getting venues to welcome
OL,14,FGypsy, Roma and Travellers in.
