OL,3,C'We have a vibrant culture but it's
OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,F"We've just done a project in Newport
OL,8,Frecently at The Riverfront theatre and
OL,9,Fthey have a very inclusive policy
OL,10,Fwhere over two hundred and fifty Roma
OL,11,Fpeople come in to use their space, but
OL,12,Fit's very rare to get spaces that will
OL,13,Fwelcome Gypsy, Roma and Travellers.
OL,15,F"There is that negative perception of
OL,16,Fthe communities. Ultimately we want to
OL,17,Fhave a mainstream presence, we don't
OL,18,Fjust want to be forgotten and hidden
OL,19,Faway, we have a vibrant culture that
OL,20,Fwe want to share and celebrate."
