OL,7,FThe tour also features artist-led
OL,8,Fworkshops which aims to further
OL,9,Fexplain themes within the show and
OL,10,Feducate audiences.
OL,12,FDaniel Baker is an artist and curator
OL,13,Fwho is currently curating the Gypsy
OL,14,FMaker programme for the Romani Culture
OL,15,Fand Arts Company.
OL,17,F"The programme is unique in
OL,18,Fcommissioning new work from Gypsy,
OL,19,FRoma and Traveller artists." He said.
