OL,7,FDr Rosamaria Kostic Cisneros is an
OL,8,Fartist and researcher. She is showing
OL,9,Fscreen dance work at the exhibition -
OL,10,Ftwo films of dances that she has
OL,11,Fcreated.
OL,13,F"It's been two dance films that are
OL,14,Frepresenting my Roma dance background
OL,15,Fand also include my two daughters",
OL,16,Fshe explained.
