OL,3,C'We have a vibrant culture but it's
OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,F"Both pieces are inclusive and the
OL,8,Fhope is that they are accessible - one
OL,9,Fpiece includes BSL embedded in there
OL,10,Fand there's a bit of looking at the
OL,11,Fflamenco tradition, but also changing
OL,12,Fthat and trying to challenge some of
OL,13,Fthe traditional ways of doing things."
OL,15,FDr Rosamaria said she is "really
OL,16,Fpushing myself as an artist but also
OL,17,Fpushing gallery spaces to include
OL,18,Fdance works and screen dance works
OL,19,Fthat are representative of the Roma
OL,20,Fculture identity."
