OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,FIn addition to this, her films are
OL,8,Flooking at the environmental climate
OL,9,Fcrisis.
OL,11,F"In the first work, we were looking at
OL,12,Fdeforestation and in the second work
OL,13,Fwe were looking at plastic consumption
OL,14,Fand microplastics and how and what we
OL,15,Fcan do. And both films are asking us
OL,16,F'what kind of ancestors do we want to
OL,17,Fbe?'
