OL,3,C'We have a vibrant culture but it's
OL,4,Cvery rare to get spaces that welcome
OL,5,Cus'
OL,7,F"And that's why my daughters were
OL,8,Fembedded in that because it's central
OL,9,Fto who we are as a culture, as a
OL,10,Fcommunity, our environment. A lot of
OL,11,Fmy work is respecting traditions,
OL,12,Fhonouring the body and thinking about
OL,13,Fpolitical issues."
OL,15,FShe added: "There are always barriers.
OL,16,FI've learned to use those barriers to
OL,17,Fhelp me challenge people through love
OL,18,Fand kindness."
